text: Muravey () is a rural locality (a village) in Kazadayevsky Selsoviet, Sterlitamaksky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 218 as of 2010. There are 5 streets. == Geography == It is located 11 km from Sterlitamak, 2 km from Novoye Baryatino. == References == Category:Rural localities in Sterlitamaksky District
title: Muravey, Bashkortostan
